# Run "rake doc:app" to generate API documentation for your models, controllers, helpers, and libraries.
This is a cornerstone app consisting of the following setup:

   sqlite3 as main database store for active resource objects
   Devise for Authentication; CanCan for Authorization
   
   Slim for views; formtastic for drop forms
   Capistrano for deployment

   Shoulda for tests; Rspec for additional testing and documentation, along with annotate-models

   ruby-prof for profiling, ruby-debug for debuging
